<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />But you, Lord, are a merciful and gracious God,</para>

<para style="q1">slow to anger, and abundant in covenant faithfulness and trustworthiness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />Turn toward me and have mercy on me;</para>

<para style="q1">give your strength to your servant;</para>

<para style="q1">save the son of your servant woman.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />Show me a sign of your favor.</para>

<para style="q1">Then those who hate me will see it and be put to shame</para>

<para style="q1">because you, Yahweh, have helped me and comforted me.</para>
